   <publicationStmt>
    <p>Second web edition, 2024</p>
   </publicationStmt>
   <sourceDesc>
    <p>This is an enhanced and extended version of the catalogue of Lacy's Acting Edition originally
     created by the 
     now sadly defunct <ref target="https://web.archive.org/web/20051120153123/http://www.worc.ac.uk/victorian/victorianplays/lacys.htm">Victorian Plays Project</ref>, directed  by Dr Richard Pearson at the University of Worcester.
     <!-- 
     archived at<ref target="http://victorian.nuigalway.ie/modx/index.php?id=64">the VPP_website at
     NUI Galway</ref>.--></p>
    <p>The catalogue has been cross-checked against several other sources of information. Various
     minor errors and inconsistencies have been corrected, and additional information added,
     particularly about available digitizations of the plays.</p>
   </sourceDesc></fileDesc></teiHeader>

